        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="IilbE9co8Z_d94cJzwjW-37" value="The Cloud Administrator makes a change to the cloud such as creating a new network or a new VM.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Note&lt;/b&gt;: To ensure that the cloud API service is functioning properly, open up port 443 for HTTPS connectivity and configure your firewalls accordingly." style="text;strokeColor=none;align=left;fillColor=none;html=1;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
